{"tid":794840,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【爆相爆片】大圍買餸撞一撞 港母女腳踢棍打內地姐","createTime":"2018-08-26T14:16:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-26T22:48:46.000Z","uid":73915,"like":71,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"646320dd47347abf73d1b3acea7498fd523eca7b","tid":794840,"uid":73915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T14:16:03.000Z","msg":"估唔到買餸都可以變成拳頭交。讀者冼女士噚日(25日)下晝5點半喺大圍街巿外圍買餸期間，睇到一對港人母女同另一名操普通話嘅女人，因為街頭碰撞問題嘈起上嚟，雙方一言不合，普通話女人一嘢捉住港女件衫大鬧，對方大叫縮手，繼而就兜腳踢落對方個小腹，然後港女阿媽見到，加入戰團用拐仗加多一招「鐵拐李」送畀對方。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180826/58610405\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180826%2F58610405&d=Y%2FW%2FCsZJIoYQ15%2FbMY8nJ8VakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=7aa14dc7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180826%2F58610405&h=709bb09f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180826/58610405</a>"},{"pid":"972b84d33e89f81cac6689e572f9831852a91ab5","tid":794840,"uid":20222,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T14:19:08.000Z","msg":"做得好呀"},{"pid":"631773ceb9d269a480f750f3ae921f57a8283e21","tid":794840,"uid":94828,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T14:20:01.000Z","msg":"香港義士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"672c2b5b3f6f556762c5a8e33c9c637acd19dbd4","tid":794840,"uid":36184,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T14:33:07.000Z","msg":"往死裡打"},{"pid":"db2e49a58a60a400fb91c5410d4a592fefb64d28","tid":794840,"uid":53798,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T14:33:10.000Z","msg":"用武力最快解決呢d問題"},{"pid":"02921d2ffdeda3de03ed9b8d80062ffdd618b69b","tid":794840,"uid":33481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T14:33:59.000Z",